summer  Preference will be given to cadets who will be presenting their research at a conference    Previous  Welcome Next  SURI 2015   Last Updated  Apr 7  2016 8 19 PM URL  http libguides vmi edu c php g 232197 Print Page Login to LibApps Report a problem 